trans-unit.source: Replication of Model II from Jin et al (2001)

This package implements Model II from the Structure of Growing Social Networks (Jin et al, 2001). It generates a social network, using three processes: 1) random friendships, 2) friends meeting friends, and 3) dissolution. I wrote it to generate a static network structure. I did not write it as a scaffold for dynamic simulations. A java port exists as well, since the Python code is terribly slow.
trans-unit.target: 该软件包从不断发展的社交网络的结构中实现了模型II （Jin等，2001）。它使用三个过程生成一个社交网络：1）随机的友谊，2）结识朋友和3）解散。我写它来生成静态网络结构。我没有将其写为动态仿真的支架。还存在一个Java端口，因为Python代码非常慢。
